<p>"I think us women need to stick together to break the barriers and push these topics so far that eventually, nobody would even question 'alternative' life choices that are out of our control anymore."</p>
<p>我认为我们女性需要团结起来，打破障碍，以致于没有人会质疑我们都没办法控制的“另类”的生活选择。</p>
<p>成熟而完整的女人 vs 也是成熟而完整的女人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201123/1b3ea1c1bb2c4a8b9b1a93f7e0582f70.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>Life choices don't range from wrong to right based on societal expectations. No matter how you decide to live your life, or no matter what life decides for you, give everyone else respect and compassion, because we’re all doing our best.</p>
<p>人生的选择不会因为社会的期望而有错有对。无论你决定如何生活，或无论生活给你怎样的决定，给别人足够的尊重和同情，因为我们都在尽力。</p>
<p>你现在唯一的工作就是不疯掉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201123/f94c758928684c04acd9249d0d0e1f21.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>某人不太好的样子 vs 也是某人不太好的样子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201123/310a5a8b13ab461e89952c0f6ce5d18d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>理想身材就像时尚趋势一样在变化。做自己就好。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201123/c76aa058008f4920854f902135328b08.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>希望我看起来这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201123/78e2574fbb3247edb848b1254c41077f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>你自由啦</p>
